snippet.title: Tales of the Black Death - PC trailer
snippet.description:
Tales of the Black Death.
an interactive narrative set in the middle ages.

Soon available on steam.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1590000/Tales_of_the_Black_Death/

The trailer feature the music of composer Nicolas Gasparini
more of his work can be found here
https://thedarkpiano.com/
